<br>
Ive noticed that almost 99% of the people that play this game have a horrible problem with mob mentality.  You guys cannot WAIT for the next person to fuck up and run em through the ringer.  If someone tries to see the other side, you run them through the ringer too...its kinda sad.  It always makes me think of the witch scene in Monty Python.  <br>
<br>
One person shouts witch! then the entire QC community comes running and shouting with pitch forks in the air, with one person already getting the fire goin to burn em at the stake.  When all along, all the guy did was have a fake witch nose on.<br>
<br>
guilt by association is a pretty flimsy argument.  If im in a gas station, and i happen to have went to highschool, and maybe was study partners at one time with the guy that is now holding up said gas-station...am i a guilty party to the crime?  If one member of the siera club dropped a piece of trash on the ground, is the sierra club now defunct?  <br>
<br>
oh..btw THIS IS A VIDEO GAME!! <br>
