<br>
Some feel that by continuing to associate yourself with a miscreant, you are either activily or tacitly condoning (or at least allowing) the actions of that miscreant.  With the absence of public censure,  there really can be no way for those outside the assocation to tell if you do or not.<br>
<br>
<br>
AT THE VERY LEAST, you should not be surprised if someone who doesn't know you but knows (at least) OF him treats you with suspicion because you, the unknown, fly the same tag as him, the known miscreant.  <br>
